description: In her final day on the stand in the trial against Sean “Diddy” Combs, Cassie, whose real name is Casandra Ventura, spoke about the day he attacked her in a hotel hallway in 2016, saying he was “black out” at the time of the assault from drugs and alcohol. The cross-examination on Friday focused on Ventura’s allegation that Combs raped her in 2018, which he has denied. NBC’s Chloe Melas reports for Saturday TODAY.
title: Cassie wraps up her testimony in Diddy's sex trafficking trial
